data.title: Campbell County, city of Lynchburg, Virginia : 1:50 000-scale topographic map
data.meta_description: Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Title in margin: Campbell County, city of Lynchburg, Va. Includes location map, index to 1:24 000-scale maps, and conversion table. "37079-C1-CF-050." Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image.
